name: Hollow Pixels 7 - Doll
description:
From another natural association, this creature was named « Doll ». 
One might try to figure out how it is feeling based on its look, but let’s keep in mind that our human emotions only apply to us. 
Does it feel the same emotions but show them differently or does it feels entirely different emotions? 
This is one question we might be able to answer as we explore the Hollow Pixels world. 

IG&Twitter:  @dacosta_works
